<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Vedda_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: History">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="History">History</span></h2>
<table width="300" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="1" style="float: right; margin: 0 0 1em 1em; font-size: 80%; background-color: ##F0F8FF; border: 1px solid #cccccc;">
<tr>
<td colspan="2" align="center" bgcolor="#99CCCC"><big><b>Ebb and flow of the Vedda in Sri Lanka</b></big><br />
(28000 BCE&#160;–&#160;2000 CE)<br /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>First inhabitants of Ceylon, presumed ancestors of the Vedda</td>
<td>(28000 BCE)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Immigration of <a href="/wiki/Iron_Age" title="Iron Age">Iron Age</a> culture with unknown language</td>
<td>(1000 BCE)</td>
