<tr>
<td>Introduction of <a href="/wiki/Prakrits" title="Prakrits" class="mw-redirect">Prakrits</a> by Indian settlers</td>
<td>(500 BCE)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Withdrawal of Veddas to the <a href="/wiki/Malaya_Rata" title="Malaya Rata">Central Highlands</a></td>
