<td>(1100–1300)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Expansion of Vedda Creole into <a href="/wiki/Uva_Province" title="Uva Province" class="mw-redirect">Uva Province</a>, <a href="/wiki/Rajarata" title="Rajarata">Rajarata</a> and <a href="/wiki/Eastern_Province,_Sri_Lanka" title="Eastern Province, Sri Lanka">Eastern Province</a>.</td>
<td>(1300–1900)</td>
