</tr>
</table>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Vedda_language&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Numerals">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Numerals">Numerals</span></h3>
<p>These are found in definite and indefinite forms. <i>ekama</i> one (def.) and <i>ekamak</i> once (indef.) They count ekamay, dekamay and tunamay. Vedda also reduces the numer formations found in Sinhalese.</p>
<table class="wikitable">
